title: Jean Michel Jarre discography FLAC
description:
these are all of Jean Michel Jarre&#039;s albums i managed to collect in FLAC format.
they do sound better than any mp3, provided you have a good sound system.
Deserted palace and Musique pour supermarche are included in mp3 form, as they are more difficult to find.

I could not find every album, but i&#039;m still searching.
If you find any album that is not here, in FLAC format, please post a link, or turn it into a torrent and post it on TPB, and then post a link.
this torrent will be deleted as more material becomes available, and replaced with an updated one.
therefore, you must check this page periodically. if the torrent is replaced, download the new one, save to the same location, do a hash-check and you can resume. existing files will not be changed.

also, i think it&#039;s common courtesy to upload as much as you download. don&#039;t hit and run...

seeding will be done at 100 KB/s, using Azureus. RC4 encryption is mandatory.


enjoy ;-)
